column1: Style Home Ultra Cozy Large Sofa
column3: The sofa has a short back rest but a long width to get lazy while sitting lazy. With a matte fabric finish and a soft center, this is the perfect sofa to indulge someone to get lazy and stay back.

This smooth synthetic is perfect for lounge environment, and is stain proof. It is as easy as wiping stain off it with a wipe, thus reducing maintenance. It is built tough so that it does not tear or break easily.
A very snug sofa set with a 3 seat sofa and a divan. Ideal for placing along corner of your large living room. Watch TV while enjoying the company of your friends and family in this giant sofa set.
